  'lab.p10_logic_theory': 'Asli electronic circuits mein, logic gates continuous voltages process karte hain. TTL (Transistor-Transistor Logic) khaas voltage thresholds define karta hai.',
  'lab.p10_logic_theory2': 'HIGH (1): 2.0V se 5.0V ke darmiyan | LOW (0): 0.0V se 0.8V ke darmiyan | Undefined: 0.8V se 2.0V ke darmiyan',
