  'lab.p11_fluid_theory_p2': '<strong>Neutral Buoyancy:</strong> Jab submarine ka total weight (ballast samet) buoyant force ke bilkul barabar ho jata hai. <br/> <code>Fg = Fb</code> ➔ <code>(m_sub + m_ballast)g = ρVg</code>',
